0e9a57f9f\"><strong>Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"51e5fb56-c4f1-4bcd-ae0b-bac64fa6efa9\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"c5b1b451-9474-4afc-a147-7abb2b3914b5\"><strong>Reembolso parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"9f561b43-4a14-4021-875d-2cf4ed4b6ada\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"ab7efb01-7e12-4c3e-8e97-3e21f1b69fcf\"><strong>Múltiples reembolsos parciales</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"7bfba827-4346-466b-967f-96e5c3815401\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"79e9de91-89e5-461a-a976-bdccee4a4dd7\"><strong>Validez del Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"980f78d2-e091-426e-a79f-83c85cb968ee\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"me146rno-utre76-161\"><strong>Datos del Cliente requeridos por el Banco*</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><ul data-block-id=\"me146u2r-frr8w4-164\"><li data-block-id=\"me146u2r-uwvmul-165\"><p data-block-id=\"me146tsx-14dgy0-163\">Número de Teléfono Móvil</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f8270e5-fafe-4128-abe3-b85f9c67e07d\"><strong>Integración compatible</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"01aa413c-90f2-4b3e-8a19-924838f3f649\">Payment API, Payment Session, Subscription, Recurring</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"me1476g6-tjxxn3-176\">*El Banco validará la credencial de inicio de sesión con el número de teléfono móvil enviado durante la Solicitud de Pago (Payment Request)</p><h2 data-block-id=\"cfdaf3d6-9051-4523-8aaa-f70aa85edcd9\">Flujo de Vinculación de Cuenta (Account Linking flow)</h2><p data-block-id=\"me13tcxt-m1ubc8-147\">El cliente final selecciona el banco para vincular en la página de pago (checkout page) y procesa la autorización (Account Linking)</p><p data-block-id=\"me149cxs-b6lkkf-190\"><img data-block-id=\"me14kcs5-v502uk-216\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Payment%20session%20-%20DD%20linking.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"275\" height=\"335\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:275px;height:335px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"me0xf87f-gez1lt-073\"><img data-block-id=\"me1i3s02-0d0ezx-028\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/SCB%20DD.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab></p>","SeoTitle":"SCB Direct Debit","Description":null}]